<p>9. Russinovich, M., Costa, M., Fournet, C., Chisnall, D., Delignat-Lavaud, A., Clebsch, S., Vaswani, K., Bhatia, V. 2021. Toward confidential cloud computing. <i>Communications of the ACM</i> 64(6), 54–61; <a href="https://dl.acm.org/doi/10.1145/3453930">https://dl.acm.org/doi/10.1145/3453930</a>.</p>
